The paper discusses the deployment of femtocells in indoor environments to improve signal quality and data-rate communications. This topic falls under the category of networked systems and communication, which is covered by cs.NI (Networked Systems), making it the most likely category. The paper also discusses interference management and throughput analysis, which are topics covered by cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The proposed on-demand scheme for femtocell deployment involves self-organization and system optimization, which are topics covered by cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Therefore, the five likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SY, and cs.CR.
